5102.html" class="D(b) Pos(r)" data-ylk="sec:channel-latest;slk:Engadget Podcast: Why the PlayStation Portal is truly baffling;elm:hdln;ct:story;aid:33271349-7949-4411-a1ce-f45a63a99129;itc:0;cpos:6;pos:1"><img class="Pos(r) W(300px) W(200px)--lg W(100%)--sm D(b) Trsp(a) Trsdu(300ms) Op(0.8):h H(a)" loading="eager" alt="Engadget Podcast" src="https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/NXDkCjtjETbYvPJT7iJXgA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQyMTtweW9mZj0wO3c9NjQwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/c8e851c0-2b3d-11eb-baea-6c6fe29971fb.cf.jpg" width="640" height="421"/></a><div class="Pos(r) D(f) Ai(st) Mstart(25px) Mstart(0)--sm Mb(0)--sm"><div class="Px(20px)--sm Py(15px)--sm Bgc(white)--sm W(100%)--sm"><div class="D(f) Fld(c) Ai(fs)" data-component="PostInfo"><h2 class="My(0)"><a href="/engadget-podcast-playstation-portal-review-133055102.html" class="C(engadgetSteelGray)  Fw(400) Td(n) Bdbw(1px):h Bdbc(lightgrey):h Bdbs(s):h Fz(30px) Lh(35px) Fz(22px)--lg Lh(25px)--lg Fz(24px)--md Lh(30px)--md Fz(22px)--sm Lh(25px)--sm Fw(500)!--sm serif" data-ylk="sec:channel-latest;slk:Engadget Podcast: Why the PlayStation Portal is truly baffling;elm:hdln;ct:story;aid:33271349-7949-4411-a1ce-f45a63a99129;itc:0;cpos:6;pos:2">Engadget Podcast: Why the PlayStation Portal is truly baffling</a></h2><div class="Mt(10px) Fz(15px) Lh(20px) D(n)--sm serif C(engadgetFontBlack)">It&#x27;s not the Vita successor we were looking for.</div><div class="Mt(15px) D(f) Ai(c) Fz(14px)"><div class="Mend(7px)"><a alt="Opens Devindra Hardawar webpage" href="/about/editors/devindra-hardawar/" class="D(f) Ai(c) Td(n)" data-ylk="sec:channel-latest;slk:Devindra Hardawar;elm:author;itc:0"><img alt="Devindra Hardawar" src="https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/JuNGHqVTz1GMmB_nx8qB_w--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTYwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz02MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blogcdn.com%2Fwww.engadget.com%2Fmedia%2F2016%2F03%2Fdevindra-engadget-headshot-small.jpg&amp;co